    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Testing a hypothesis or model. In science and related fields, refers to testing systematically under controlled conditions in order to discover the qualities, behavior, or effects of the subject of the experiment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
